A \strong{free NASA Earthdata Login} account is required
(\url{https://urs.earthdata.nasa.gov}). Set credentials in one of two ways:
\itemize{
\item \strong{Environment variables} (recommended):
\preformatted{Sys.setenv(EARTHDATA_USER = "my_user",
