\item \strong{\code{.netrc} file} (for pipelines), then pass its path via
\code{netrc_path}:
\preformatted{machine urs.earthdata.nasa.gov login my_user password my_pass}
}
After registering, activate GES DISC access at
\url{https://disc.gsfc.nasa.gov/earthdata-login}.
